{"type": "article", "id": 14962, "title": "HOMMAGE collection", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-16T07:29:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140612lNIWQpLsZqJ0rzjR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自日本设计师 Ryo Kashiwazaki 主导的品牌 Hender Scheme，他们挑选了一些经典款，组成 HOMMAGE collection 并在台湾品牌 plain-me 上出售。这双鞋原皮养色鞋以 New Blance 1300 为原型，采用不经染色的猪皮和牛皮缝制，随着时间的改变，颜色也会发生变化，拥有属于私人的感受。在保留原本运动风格的基础上，赋予了一份时尚感。<a href=\"http://www.plain-me.com/brands/allbrands/henderscheme/brand.asp?conditiontype=3&amp;poids=121\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142339GP65oCKF8aH0mJnB.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"685\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66894531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142339ps0BMAHvX2FDICq6.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"685\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66894531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}